         <abstract>
            <p>A cell-vertex finite volume approximation of elliptic convection-dominated diffusion equations is considered in two dimensions. The scheme is shown to be stable and second-order convergent in a mesh-dependent L&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;-norm.</p>
          </abstract>
